    <briefdescription>
<para>Face Landmarking and Normalization Pipeline (Layer 2 - Native). </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Implements FacePipeline using OpenCV&apos;s FaceDetectorYN (YuNet) face landmarker. Resolves 5 facial landmarks, applies perspective affine warps to neutralize face roll/scale rotation, extracts eye crops, and estimates 3D camera coordinates via solvePnP. </para>
